      "id": "PopularPost204198",
      "post_content": "Rather than playing in red, this seems like something you'd splash in blue control.[Levitation](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Levitation) can keep your guys out of the Mudslide. Throw in something like an [Icy Manipulator](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Icy Manipulator) and you'll really slow people down.  \nThrow some white into it and you can drop [Sunblast Angel](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sunblast Angel) for some mass graveyard filling.  \nBe creative.",
